ISLAMABAD, Nov 4 (APP): Minister for Power Division Omar Ayub Khan Wednesday directed the Power Secretary to refer the Rs 80 billion misappropriation of funds case by PML-N government to Federal Investigation Agency (FIA).
In a tweet, the minister have directed Secretary Power to refer the Rs80 billion diversion of funds by the PML-N government in Nandipur Power Plant earmarked for PSO fuel payment to construction and covering losses in fuel to FIA.
